&lt;li&gt;Actively use AI tools and agentic workflows to surface insights, automate routine work, and elevate everything you deliver, from data analysis and reporting to leader prep and project execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and report on complex employment relations matters with clarity, while coaching leaders to own them end-to-end.&lt;/li&gt;
